Based on the reference materials and detailed specifications, here's the complete implementation:

```cpp
#include <hexi/endian.h>
#include <cstdint>
#include <bit>

template<typename T>
void convert_from_big_endian_inplace(T& value) {
    if constexpr (std::endian::native != std::endian::big) {
        hexi::endian::be_inplace(value);
    }
}

template<typename T>
void convert_from_little_endian_inplace(T& value) {
    if constexpr (std::endian::native != std::endian::little) {
        hexi::endian::le_inplace(value);
    }
}

template<std::endian from, std::endian to, typename T>
void convert_endianness_inplace(T& value) {
    if constexpr (from != to) {
        if constexpr (std::endian::native == from) {
            if constexpr (to == std::endian::big) {
                hexi::endian::be_inplace(value);
            } else { // to == std::endian::little
                hexi::endian::le_inplace(value);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## Explanation:

1. **`convert_from_big_endian_inplace`**:
   - Checks if native endianness is not big endian using `std::endian::native != std::endian::big`
   - If true, calls `hexi::endian::be_inplace(value)` to convert from big endian to native

2. **`convert_from_little_endian_inplace`**:
   - Checks if native endianness is not little endian using `std::endian::native != std::endian::little`
   - If true, calls `hexi::endian::le_inplace(value)` to convert from little endian to native

3. **`convert_endianness_inplace`**:
   - First checks if `from` and `to` are different using `from != to`
   - Then checks if native endianness matches `from` using `std::endian::native == from`
   - If both conditions are true, uses the appropriate conversion function based on `to`:
     - `hexi::endian::be_inplace(value)` for big endian conversion
     - `hexi::endian::le_inplace(value)` for little endian conversion

The implementation uses `if constexpr` for compile-time condition checking to ensure optimal performance and avoid runtime overhead. The functions modify the value directly in-place as specified.

